data.description: ! Updates ! Check out the new photos in the listing! Introducing 272 Scenic Drive, McDonough, GA.  Recently updated with fresh paint and new flooring, this home exudes a comfortable, welcoming atmosphere. The glassed-in porch provides a serene spot to enjoy views of the private wooded yard, which opens to a peaceful community lake. With 9-foot and vaulted ceilings, the interior feels spacious and open. A striking floor-to-ceiling stone fireplace graces the living space, adding a touch of warmth and character. The kitchen features elegant granite counters, seamlessly combining style and functionality. Nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac, this residence offers a sense of privacy and calm. Opportunities like this are limited, so don't miss out on making this gem your own!
